<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Photo Day Registration Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #E9F9EE;"
  >
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <p>
        Hi
        {{parentFirstName}},
      </p>

      <p>
        Thank you for registering
        {{childFirstName}}
        for photo day at
        <br />
        <span style="color: #111827; font-weight: bold;">{{centreName}}</span>.
      </p>

      <p>
        We’re so happy you’re interested in our photos — we can’t wait to
        capture some beautiful memories of
        {{childFirstName}}!
      </p>

      <h3 style="color: #111827">Registration Details:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Child's Name:</strong></td><td
          >{{childFirstName}} {{childLastName}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Date:</strong></td><td
          >{{photoDay}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Room:</strong></td><td
          >{{room}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Parent's Name:</strong></td><td
          >{{parentFirstName}} {{parentLastName}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong></td><td
          >{{parentEmail}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Phone:</strong></td><td
          >{{parentPhone}}</td></tr>

        {{#if siblingFirstName}}
          <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Sibling's Name:</strong></td><td
            >{{siblingFirstName}} {{siblingLastName}}</td></tr>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if message}}
          <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Message:</strong></td><td
            >{{message}}</td></tr>
        {{/if}}

        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Permission to Share:</strong></td><td
          >{{permissionToShare}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Family Photos:</strong></td><td
          >{{familyPhotos}}</td></tr>
      </table>

      {{#if siblingFirstName}}
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #111827; font-weight: bold;">
          Just a heads-up about sibling photos</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 14px;">
          Sibling sessions are photographed separately from your child’s
          individual portraits, so they’ll come in their own gallery with
          different package options. This helps keep everything neat and easy to
          navigate when you’re choosing your photos!
        </p>
      {{/if}}

      {{#if (eq familyPhotos "yes")}}
        <p>
          We also appreciate your interest in family photography! We’ll be in
          touch soon with more information on how we can create meaningful
          family moments outside the centre environment.
        </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
        If we need anything further, we’ll be sure to reach out. Until then,
        we’re looking forward to seeing your little one on photo day at
        <span style="color: #111827; font-weight: bold;">{{centreName}}</span>
        on
        <span style="color: #111827; font-weight: bold;">{{photoDay}}</span>!
      </p>

      <p>
        Warm regards,<br />The Little Lens Team
      </p>

      <img
        src="https://littlelens.com.au/logos/logo.png"
        alt="Little Lens Logo"
        style="max-width: 200px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
      />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>